{"tid":483145,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"三國無雙真人電影再有新相！ 姜皓文扮張角超神似？","createTime":"2017-11-29T00:12:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-29T04:35:47.000Z","uid":33359,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c960a656fe97b4370c301914484745d2ca6332e6","tid":483145,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:12:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_00_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_00_1024.jpg&h=3b1ab82c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n自從《真．三國無雙》真人電影版在新西蘭開鏡後，其三國無雙的人物造型即相繼曝光，除了之前林雪飾演的董卓，已叫人有深刻印象之外，最近在導演周顯揚的微博之中，又有新角色造型曝光，就是由姜皓文飾演黃巾軍頭目天公將軍張角！<br />\n<br />\n只見姜皓文所扮演的張角有著白色的眉毛，以及白色的山羊鬚，雖與三國無雙張角的星字髮型不同，但其造型亦是維妙維肖。此外，曝光的造型還包括了由古天樂飾演的呂布造型、騎著馬由王凱飾演的曹操、韓庚飾演的關羽，以及雙劍造型由楊祐寧飾演的劉備。另外，也見到羅家英出現在電影組當中，而他將會飾演曹操早年的好友呂伯奢。<br />\n<br />\n【精選消息】2 千萬年後人類進化成一個球？<br />\n<br />\n【精選消息】網民投訴！一田美少女戰士家居服貨不對辦<br />\n<br />\n不過，網民對於三國無雙電影版的造型就唔多 buy，更留言表示拍三國無雙唔用三國無雙嘅衫，已經係一大敗筆！又謂見到瘦弱的關公，直言是關公災難。而青靚白淨的曹操，亦被彈沒有梟雄味。此外，網民見到羅家英，更笑謂會否被唐三藏騎劫。大家又怎樣看這些選角及造型呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_01_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_01_600.jpg&h=c3c16967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姜皓文飾演的張角造型曝光。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_03_600.jpg&h=2ffaf7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n古天樂飾演呂布。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_03_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_03_600.jpg&h=2ffaf7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王凱飾演的曹操。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_04_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_04_600.jpg&h=5b621e77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n韓庚飾演的關羽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/1955000/1957849/171128_San_05_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1955000%2F1957849%2F171128_San_05_600.jpg&h=c0c75218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雙劍造型的劉備，由楊祐寧飾演。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">據指羅家英將飾演呂伯奢。</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957849#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fezone.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Farticle%2F1957849%23%26gid%3D1%26pid%3D2&d=KrzM3%2B12F8yz3rimzNYpnOPnIAwyWqphGIcg0J4V%2Buw%3D&h=1d73ad4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://ezone.ulifestyle.com.hk/article/1957849#&amp;gid=1&amp;pid=2</a>"},{"pid":"5658db9851adb5482819e5fb302f0b04b30fac24","tid":483145,"uid":31836,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:17:59.000Z","msg":"樓主呂布圖呢"},{"pid":"743048d83e8ef6419183522354421b3a6d1084cc","tid":483145,"uid":65144,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"真三國無雙電影版 姜皓文飾演張角<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/482330/1?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/482330/1?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nold new is so 唔識串"},{"pid":"7ae85406e44dc429e3ed5b41076d4058a484c623","tid":483145,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T00:32:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"p